{"body": [{"indent": 0, "text": ["Rust Perforation"], "type": "title", "extent": [59, 80], "level": 0}, {"indent": 0, "type": "summary", "extent": [80, 137], "text": ["Simulates a rusty, possibly perforated material."]}, {"indent": 0, "type": "para", "extent": [137, 201], "text": ["This operator simulates a rusty, possibly perforated material."]}, {"indent": 0, "type": "para", "extent": [201, 327], "text": ["You will first generate a material that outputs a color, then pipe its\noutput into the Surface Color input of this operator."]}, {"indent": 0, "type": "para", "extent": [327, 513], "text": ["The rust and perforation thresholds control the contribution of each\nstage of corrosion, and represent good candidates for animation at the\nshader level if tied to Parameter operators."]}, {"indent": 0, "type": "para", "extent": [513, 1043], "text": ["If the Surface Position (", {"text": ["P"], "type": "code"}, ") and Surface Color (", {"text": ["Cf"], "type": "code"}, ") inputs are not\nconnected, the global variables by the same name will be used instead.\nTypically, you will use ", {"text": ["Rest Position"], "fullpath": "/nodes/vop/restpos", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/vop/restpos"}, " or ", {"text": ["UV Space Change"], "fullpath": "/nodes/vop/uvspacechg", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/vop/uvspacechg"}, " as inputs for\n", {"text": ["P"], "type": "code"}, ", and any operator that yields a lit color, such as ", {"text": ["Shiny Metal"], "fullpath": "/nodes/vop/shinymetal", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/vop/shinymetal"}, " or\n", {"text": ["Lighting Model"], "fullpath": "/nodes/vop/lighting", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/vop/lighting"}, ", as inputs for ", {"text": ["Cf"], "type": "code"}, ". If you need to access the global\nvariables directly, they are available from the ", {"text": ["Global Variables"], "fullpath": "/nodes/vop/global", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/vop/global"}, "\noperator."]}, {"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 4, "blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "extent": [1052, 1078], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/vop/cavities", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/vop/cavities"}]}, {"indent": 4, "blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "extent": [1078, 1102], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/vop/global", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/vop/global"}]}, {"indent": 4, "blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "extent": [1102, 1128], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/vop/lighting", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/vop/lighting"}]}, {"indent": 4, "blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "extent": [1128, 1150], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/vop/mold", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/vop/mold"}]}, {"indent": 4, "blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "extent": [1150, 1179], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/vop/shinymetal", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/vop/shinymetal"}]}], "container": true, "type": "bullet_group"}], "indent": 0, "level": 1, "text": "Related", "role": "section", "extent": [1043, 1052], "container": true, "type": "related_section", "id": "related"}], "summary": ["Simulates a rusty, possibly perforated material."], "type": "root", "attrs": {"version": null, "namespace": null, "internal": "rust", "context": "vop", "type": "node", "icon": "VOP/rust"}, "title": ["Rust Perforation"]}